### **3. 22_LogPulseDetector**  
**Description:**  
A tool that detects bursts of error messages or warnings from system logs.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogPulseDetector - Log Frequency Scanner

LogPulseDetector finds clusters of similar messages in logs that may indicate a recurring issue or attack attempt.

## Features
- Detects message frequency  
- Highlights unique lines  
- Works on rotated logs  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/22_LogPulseDetector.git
cd 22_LogPulseDetector
python analyze.py /var/log/syslog
